# Day 4 - Pandas Basics

##  Objective
Learn the basics of Pandas and how it is used for data manipulation and analysis in Python.

---

## Topics Covered

- Introduction to Pandas
- Series and DataFrames
- Viewing and exploring data
- Basic operations on data

---

##  What I Practiced

- Created Pandas Series and DataFrames
- Loaded datasets using `pd.read_csv()`
- Used functions like:`.head()`
- Selected and filtered data

---

##  What I Learned

- Pandas makes working with data easier and faster  
- DataFrames are powerful for handling structured data  
- Useful for data cleaning and analysis  

